    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-03-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-03-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="60" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d60">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thurston</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hawaiian Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington D.
                                        C.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 23,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: In my communication to you under date of
                            January 20 last the statement was made that “the British commissioner in
                            Honolulu, Mr. Hawes, has called upon the Hawaiian Government to give him
                            assurances that no capital punishment will be inflicted upon the
                            insurrectionists.”</p>
                <p>Fuller information from my Government concerning such matter, received
                            since the date of such communication, is to the effect that the calls of
                            Mr. Hawes on the subject of capital punishment were unofficial, and I am
                            instructed by my Government to so inform you.</p>
                <p>With renewed assurances, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">L. A. Thurston.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
